interval [Data_fields] [(p)]

Stores interval of time, 

fields: specifies intervals of time to store - YEAR, MONTH, DAY, HOUR, MINUTE, SECOND
p: defines fractional seconds precision

Formatting:

SELECT TO_CHAR(INTERVAL '15h 25m 12s', 'HH24:MI:SS');

Automatically normalizes data, e.g.: 25h -> 1d 1h
